data.description: Don't miss Washington local school district home. It is an adorable Brick Ranch home on a crawl-- no steps to deal with. Yes!!! I'm ready to move into! It has been updated for you to move into and enjoy. This home has been freshly painted,  high-end luxury flooring, new blinds, new light fixtures, outlets, switches, panel, etc. Enjoy being in this kitchen; it has been updated, has a new epoxy countertop, and has new stainless steel appliances.  Both bathrooms have been updated! Enjoy the great yard with new fence. Yard newly landscaped, also.  New roof and gutters! Cinch Home Warranty, also!
